{"tid":332644,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"菲IS黨羽或向中日施襲","createTime":"2017-07-23T07:02:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-23T18:06:24.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9b51c6e91a3628a5c5b2adc52b23efa73a02b34a","tid":332644,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T07:02:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20098700&amp;category_guid=15335&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170723\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20098700%26category_guid%3D15335%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170723&d=0tGOBxRY4gSQ%2B5tsW92GUJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=a209bcc0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20098700%26category_guid%3D15335%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170723&h=bec4c14c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20098700&amp;category_guid=15335&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170723</a><br />\n<br />\n菲IS黨羽或向中日施襲<br />\n<br />\n國際新聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170723/large/23wx2p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170723%2Flarge%2F23wx2p.jpg&h=f3ea4f4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n杜特爾特早前在馬拉維實施戒嚴。<br />\n<br />\n「伊斯蘭國」（IS）支部武裝分子在菲律賓棉蘭老島馬拉維（Marawi）作亂踏入第九周，印尼耶加達一個智庫發表報告，指當地武裝分子可能擴大戰線，向菲律賓各地以至中國、日本等亞洲多國發動類似襲擊。<br />\n衝突政策分析學院（IPAC）總監瓊斯（Sidney Jones）指，馬拉維危機不會隨菲律賓政府軍宣佈勝利而完結，「印尼及馬來西亞將面臨從棉蘭老島返國的武裝分子威脅；具有暴力及說教能力的餘眾亦將留在菲律賓」。兩武裝分子領袖同時透過社交程式Telegram，籲黨羽向中國、日本、新加坡、泰國及南韓發動襲擊，「我們有責任對抗他們，使伊斯蘭教代替這些地方的法律。他們的領袖全是反穆斯林象徵」。馬拉維之亂始於5月23日，IS在東南亞兩分支攻佔市內大部份地區。IPAC指馬拉維的武裝分子是受敍利亞IS資助。<br />\n新加坡《海峽時報》<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n\tIS敢死隊名單曝光　173死士謀襲歐洲<br />\n國際新聞 8小時前"},{"pid":"71cae9cd04dc1a96d299e63e2d6feef2744d8b2e","tid":332644,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T12:10:06.000Z","msg":"咁即係俾機會大陸用兵對菲律賓姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f0cd5a566589c1be36bc6e9bd897db6e9f3ca84","tid":332644,"uid":5715,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T15:34:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁即係俾機會大陸用兵對菲律賓姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n夠閪膽打咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc3b8992153072cd1ab914953a43629f78b0bf8c","tid":332644,"uid":40216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T15:37:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁即係俾機會大陸用兵對菲律賓姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n宜家賓賓都走左去求美佬幫手啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a70467037b798b16ed6f93fc6e0600d1e13131f","tid":332644,"uid":127447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T15:43:30.000Z","msg":"支持is炸鳩支那全國！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fedd82f12cc16a8d3e9cb33ee7a9b0cdc3c2114","tid":332644,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T16:11:23.000Z","msg":"估唔到菲律賓可以廢成咁<br />\n<br />\n打果幾百名叛軍都可以打咁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a65cf44cf68fb7dcf6b26ba01f3eb0c435ac7b39","tid":332644,"uid":113000,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T16:13:27.000Z","msg":"乜仲未打完架"},{"pid":"76e9321bec8706962458c354f9c64e139800b110","tid":332644,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T16:42:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>乜仲未打完架</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n菲律賓人質事件<br />\n幾十名特種部隊圍一個槍手, 都可以打咁耐<br />\n<br />\n家陣有800名叛軍, 至少打一年啦"},{"pid":"bf37a5917d28ed09fffb22a0c1cb2598c58e2b23","tid":332644,"uid":33481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T18:06:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>乜仲未打完架</bl